description: Before the year ends, I'm looking back, especially on the day we held our first vegan cookoff at Vegfest Pilipinas. We called this competition "Sarap Maging Vegan," It had two divisions - kids and adults, and both were such fun experiences. Maraming salamat 2022 for this moment and many moments that brought us joy. May we all continue the joy and peace in the coming new year. Happy 2023!
